---
import Icon from './Icon.astro';
---
<section class="box skills">
    <div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
        <Icon icon="server" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
        <h2>Backend Development</h2>
        <p>
            Strong experience designing and implementing scalable, high-performance server-side systems.
            Proficient in Java, Spring Boot and microservice architectures, with a focus on clean code,
            testing, and maintainability.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
        <Icon icon="globe" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
        <h2>Web Applications</h2>
        <p>
            Full-stack skills in modern web technologies: React & TypeScript on the front end,
            RESTful APIs on the back end, responsive UI design and accessibility.
            Comfortable with CI/CD workflows and end-to-end testing.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
        <Icon icon="database" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
        <h2>Data Engineering</h2>
        <p>
            Hands-on with relational and NoSQL databases (PostgreSQL, SQLite, DynamoDB) and
            data-pipeline design (ETL, batch & streaming). Skilled at data modelling,
            metrics collection and analytics for real-time insights.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>



<style>
	.box {
		border: 2px solid var(--gray-800);
		border-radius: 0.75rem;
		padding: 1.5rem;
        margin-block: 4rem;   /* 4rem au-dessus + en dessous */
        padding-inline: 1rem;
		background-color: var(--gray-999_40);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
	}

	.skills {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3rem;
	}

	.skills h2 {
		font-size: var(--text-lg);
	}

	.skills p {
		color: var(--gray-400);
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.box {
			border-radius: 1.5rem;
			padding: 2.5rem;
		}

		.skills {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
			gap: 5rem;
		}

		.skills h2 {
			font-size: var(--text-2xl);
		}
	}
</style>
